<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Congrats on Your First Listing!</title>
    <style>
        .head-con {
            width: 100%;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: green;
            color: white;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        section {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        a {
            color: green;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .whatsapp-box {
            background-color: #e0ffe0;
            border-left: 4px solid green;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="head-con">
            <h2 class="head">Thriftify</h2>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section>
        <h2>Congratulations, {{name}}! 🎉</h2>
        <p>
            You've just made your first listing on Thriftify – that's amazing! 🚀  
        </p>
       <p>
  To start selling, please update your delivery fee for each state in your profile. You can also do it quickly by clicking this link:  
  <a href="https://thriftiffy.com/create-delivery-fee" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Create Delivery Fee</a>. 🚀 or go to your profile click on edit profile and click on create delivery  
  <br/><br/>
  Without setting up your delivery fees, buyers won’t be able to purchase your items.  
  <br/>
  Need help? We're always available to assist you!
</p>

        <p>
            To increase your chances of selling quickly, here are some **pro tips** to make your listing stand out:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><b>High-Quality Photos 📸:</b> Take clear, well-lit pictures from different angles. A neat background helps buyers focus on your item.</li>
            <li><b>Accurate Descriptions ✍️:</b> Ensure your title and description match your item. Mention any flaws to build buyer trust.</li>
            <li><b>Fair Pricing 💰:</b> Research similar listings and set a competitive price.</li>
            <li><b>Promote Your Listing 📢:</b> Share your item on social media to attract more buyers!</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            Your journey as a seller has begun, and we can't wait to see you succeed. Check out your listing here:  
        </p>
        <p>
           👉 <a href="{{link}}">View My Listing</a>  
        </p>

        <div class="whatsapp-box">
            🔔 <strong>Join Our Sellers WhatsApp Group!</strong><br/>
            We’ve created a special WhatsApp group to share tips, updates, and support directly with our sellers.<br/><br/>
            👉 <a href="https://wa.me/2348163446758?text=Hi%20I%20want%20to%20join%20the%20Thriftify%20seller%20group" target="_blank">Message Us on WhatsApp</a><br/><br/>
            It's the fastest way to stay informed and get help when you need it.
        </div>

        <p>
            Need help? Feel free to reach out to our support team.  
        </p>
        <p><b>Happy Selling! 🚀</b><br>Thriftiffy Team</p>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
